targets.query: SELECT last("maxAT") FROM "jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" = 'internal' AND "application" =~ /^$Application$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(5s) fill(null)
SELECT last("count")  /5 FROM "jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" = 'all' AND "application" =~ /^$Application$/ AND "transaction" !~ /TR/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($aggregation) fill(null)
SELECT last("avg")/1000 FROM "jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" !~ /TR/ AND "application" =~ /^$Application$/ AND "statut" = 'ok') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($aggregation) fill(null)
SELECT sum("count") FROM "jmeter" WHERE (("application" =~ /^$Application$/ AND "transaction" !~ /TR/) AND "statut" = 'ko' OR "statut" = 'ok' ) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "statut"
SELECT last("maxAT") FROM "jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" = 'internal' AND "application" =~ /^$Application$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(5s) fill(null)
SELECT last("count")/5 as "Throughput" FROM "jmeter" WHERE "transaction" = 'all' AND $timeFilter AND "application" =~ /$Application/ GROUP BY time(5s) fill(null)
SELECT sum("countError") FROM "jmeter" WHERE ("transaction" = 'all' AND "application" =~ /^$Application$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s) fill(null)
SELECT sum("count") FROM "jmeter" WHERE "application" =~ /^$Application$/ AND "statut" = 'ko' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"

SELECT sum("count") as "count", mean("pct50.0") as "median", mean("pct90.0") as "90% line", mean("pct95.0") as "95% line", mean("pct99.0") as "99% line", min("min") as "min, ms", max("max") as "max, ms" FROM "jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /^$Application$/ AND "statut"='ok' AND "transaction"!~/TR/)  AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"
SELECT sum("count") FROM "jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /^$Application$/ AND "responseMessage" !~ /^$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction", "responseCode", "responseMessage"
SELECT sum("count") FROM "jmeter" WHERE "transaction" =~ /^$request$/ AND "statut" = 'all' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($aggregation) fill(null)
SELECT last("count")/5 as "Throughput" FROM "jmeter" WHERE "transaction" = 'all' AND $timeFilter AND "application" =~ /$Application/ GROUP BY time(5s) fill(null)

SELECT sum("count") as "count", mean("pct50.0") as "median", mean("pct90.0") as "90% line", mean("pct95.0") as "95% line", mean("pct99.0") as "99% line", min("min") as "min, ms", max("max") as "max, ms" FROM "jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /^$Application$/ AND "statut"='ok' AND "transaction"=~/TR/)  AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"
